videos.description: Oregon State's first touchdown is off a lateral to tight end Tuli Wily-Matagi who floats the ball to Ryan Nall for a 26 -yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Beavers' first TD is on a trick play

videos.description: Bears' Patrick Laird gets the hand off and runs up the middle for a 12-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Cal responds back with TD run

videos.description: Oregon State's Bright Ugwoegbu identifies Cal's play action pass by sacking Ross Bowers on third down.
videos.headline: Oregon State's Ugwoegbu makes nice read for sack

videos.description: Bears' Ross Bowers throws a dime and finds Vic Wharton III for a 14-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Cals' Bowers with great TD throw`

videos.description: Vic Wharton III fields the punt with a great catch and returns it 19 yards.
videos.headline: Wharton makes sweet over-the-shoulder catch on punt

videos.description: Patrick Laird finds the gap and runs for 20 yards, which puts him over the 100 yard mark for the game in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Cals' Lairds slashes through the defense for 20 yards

videos.description: Oregon State's Ryan Nall pushes through defense and barely gets the first down, which leads to a Beavers' field goal.
videos.headline: Beavers' Nall fights for first down

videos.description: Darrell Garretson gets pressured on the play and finds Noah Togiai for an Oregon State first down.
videos.headline: Garretson connects with Togiai for 25 yards

videos.description: Oregon State's head coach Corey Hall implements a new tradition by giving players who make tough and resilient plays a WWE belt on the sidelines.
videos.headline: Beavers flash new celebratory tradition

videos.description: Oregon State's Bright Ugwoegbu leaves the game due to targeting when he sacks Ross Bowers and the crown of his helmet hits his chest.
videos.headline: Beavers' Ugwoegbu ejected from game for targeting

videos.description: Cal's Patrick Laird rushes the ball and Beavers' Kee Whetzel forces a fumble and Kalani Vakameilalo recovers the ball.
videos.headline: Beavers thwart Cal drive with forced fumble

videos.description: Oregon States' Kee Whetzel sacks Cal's quarterback for a loss of 5-yards.
videos.headline: Cal's QB sacked by Beavers' Whetzel

videos.description: Beavers' Ryan Nall gets the hand off and avoids a tackle with a nice spin move for a gain of 4 yards.
videos.headline: Oregon State's Nall with nice spin move

videos.description: Quarterback Darell Garretson launches the ball to find Trevon Bradford for a 33 yard gain, putting the Beavers in scoring position.
videos.headline: Beavers' QB best throw of the game

videos.description: Great athletic touchdown by Beavers' Thomas Tyner, who receives the hand off and dodges multiple tackles.
videos.headline: Oregon State closes gap with TD

videos.description: Vic Enwere scores his first touchdown of the game on senior night.
videos.headline: Bears' rushing TD by Enwere

videos.description: Beavers' Ryan Nall hurdles over a Cal defensive player for a great offensive play.
videos.headline: Oregon State's Nall with good hurdle

videos.description: Oregon State's quarterback Darell Garretson finds Timmy Hernandez for a 34 yard gain.
videos.headline: Great catch by Beavers' Hernandez

videos.description: Patrick Laird finds multiple holes in defense making multiple cutback motions for Bears' first down and putting him over the 200 yard mark.
videos.headline: Big time run by Cal's Laird
